org.gbif.checklistbank.service

Interface DatasetImportService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DatasetImportServiceMyBatis

    public interface DatasetImportService
    Persistence service dealing with methods needed to import new checklists into checklistbank. The methods are mostly doing batch operations and larger operations, hardly any single record modifications. This interface is restricted to the mybatis module only!
